Module dev.kkorolyov.flopple
Package dev.kkorolyov.flopple.data

Class Trie<T>

java.lang.Object
dev.kkorolyov.flopple.data.Trie<T>
Type Parameters:
T - element type
public final class Trie<T>
extends java.lang.Object
A tree with nodes connected to other nodes by a given iterable element. A "terminal" node represents a complete value.
